This finally gets translated. It's been nearly a decade since it came out. Long overdue. Hope the next chapter doesn't take as long. @cammoking123: The translator translated お姉ちゃん (Onee-chan) which means literally "older sister." It's not uncommon in Japan for an older female cousin, especially when talking to a younger male cousin, to refer to herself as Onee-chan. Not to mention, in the very second page, the male character also refers to her as an older sister. It's not that the translator is retarded, it's that you don't pay attention to context, or you haven't read enough hentai manga. You should fix that, :).
